Description: ZeroClaw AI agent runtime (pre-built binary)
 Rust-based agentic AI runtime with low memory footprint (~22MB RSS on
 Raspberry Pi 4). OpenAI-compatible gateway + web dashboard on port 42617.
 .
 Configured by default for Together AI (MiniMax-M2.7 narrative, Gemma-4
 consultative). Per-skill sandboxing via Docker. See
 /etc/zeroclaw/config.toml.
 .
 This package tracks upstream prereleases (latest beta build from master)
 from the nclawzero internal apt repo.
